Ventoy2Disk.exe to create a Ventoy Sparse Image (VTSI) file.

1. Open Ventoy2Disk.exe 
2. Enable Option--->Generate VTSI File
3. Click Install button

When Generate VTSI File is enabled, Install operation will NOT write data to the disk, but will create a `VentoySparseImg.vtsi` file.
This vtsi file is the Sparse Snap of the selected disk of Ventoy.

